metadata.name: School Data #1
metadata.description:
**Upload the dream, Download the future.**         

School Data is a collection of 5555 high school girls drawn with 64*64 pixels.         
Inspired by anime and game culture, these young girls full of infinite possibilities are our exclusive pass to the metaverse!         
The ideal world is close at hand, and we will connect fantasy and reality through the power of web3.         

Return to school, Regain the power.
